{"tid":1785003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台辦追思會「勿讓手足白白犧牲」","createTime":"2019-12-16T05:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:31:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aad20990836c8994d1b974b9d027937fbbc2d626","tid":1785003,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/BIMH7YE7TOZNBMUJ7CYK2KMGCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FBIMH7YE7TOZNBMUJ7CYK2KMGCQ%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7t8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=b20aa239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191216%2FBIMH7YE7TOZNBMUJ7CYK2KMGCQ%2F&h=ff56dd80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191216/BIMH7YE7TOZNBMUJ7CYK2KMGCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n台辦追思會「勿讓手足白白犧牲」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港抗爭者梁凌杰離世半年，台灣有教會與港人昨在台北二二八紀念館外的追思牆舉辦活動，為梁凌杰默哀，並向代表他的黃色雨衣獻花，在場有人情緒激動痛哭。有份協助舉辦活動的港人台灣大學生表示，這次除了希望能向梁凌杰致悼，也想在反送中運動半年過去的時間提醒港人，不要忘記抗爭，「惟有記住這個人，才不會讓他白白犧牲」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民籲罷食藍店：一啖一滴細路血<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576425927_47dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576425927_47dd.jpg&h=73e39c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【台北】二二八紀念館外昨辦默哀活動，參與者痛哭相擁。台北濟南教會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不要有烈士才做事」<br />\n<br />\n有份協助舉辦追思活動、在台灣就讀大學五年級的港人何泳彤對《蘋果》表示，昨大概有50人出席追思活動，當中除了香港人，也有台灣人及其他國籍的參與者。台北濟南教會牧師黃春生、成功大學政治學系教授梁文韜等人致辭後，參與者為梁凌杰默禱，並向代表他的黃色雨衣獻花，隨後也有人在現場摺紙鶴。<br />\n<br />\n有參與者覺得自己不能返回香港出一分力，一度情緒激動痛哭，要其他人擁抱安慰。何泳彤稱，現場有播放《願榮光歸香港》，但當想到這首歌在梁凌杰離世後才出現，梁無法聽到該曲，自己都感到十分哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n何認為，梁凌杰是在反送中運動中，已知的第一名犧牲的抗爭者，有着他的意義，「他喚醒了香港人的抗爭意識，五大訴求是以他的遺言作為基礎去啟動」。她希望，港人不要忘記每位離世的抗爭者，因他們都是有名有姓的「手足」，同時港人不應每當出現犧牲者才醒覺，「我們不要有『烈士』才做事」。"},{"pid":"702897b1e76bde690bdc4d78dff80fe6c3df506d","tid":1785003,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咤叱歌曲投票link 👇👇👇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fmobile%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7t8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=ffba12e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/mobile/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CkEv0ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCkEv0ur.jpg&h=03b9c910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dee5fe7b83f781b1dadda7c2c6889f192a5aa26c","tid":1785003,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnDkzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnDkzda.jpg&h=97bc3868&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boyz9mA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fboyz9mA.jpg&h=681d4c